		<div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 text-center fh5co-heading">
		    <h2>Company Background</h2>
		    <p>Lehas Trading Enterprises  CC is  a  wholly and  registered  Namibian company, registration number: CC/2016/09484.</p>
		    <p>The  company  was  established  by  Mr.  Leevi Hafeni  Shigwedha, a previously  disadvantaged   Namibian   with   very   shrewd    entrepreneurship   skills   and extensive professional experience as further elaborated below.
			The company was formed to empower the youth in terms of capacity building and  skills  development.  The   entity  has   various  business  interests  and will expand in the long run as the business obtains a bigger niche in the market. </p>

		    <p>
			The company is located at 7 Von Bodenhausen Street, Pioneerspark, Windhoek-Namibia.
		    </p>
		</div>	
		<div class="container">
		    <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
