			    <img src="images/stuff.png" alt="Stuff" class="img-responsive" id="stuffImg">
			</figure>
		    </div>
		    <div class="col-md-8 col-md-push-4">
			<h2>Company Structure</h2>
			<p>Lehas Trading Enterprises CC is structured on the following strategic business units:</p>
			<figure>
			    <img src="images/struct.png" alt="Stuff" class="img-responsive" id="stuffImg">
			</figure>
			<ul>
			    <li>Consultancy services</li>
			    <li>Plumbing and electrical services</li>
			    <li>Waste management and cleaning services</li>
			    <li>Property development services</li>
			    <li>Air-conditioning and refrigeration</li>
			    <li>Information technology services</li>
			    <li>Agribusiness services</li>
			</ul>

			<p>
			    The  business units  are  designed  to  be independent structures with different operational strategies.
			    Operations  of  the  units  will  be dependent on Lehas Trading  Enterprises   CC  for  daily  operations.
			    Expertise for the business units is vast   with   the   entity   having   employees  who  have  experience  in  all  the requirements of the business.
			</p>
		    </div>
		    <div class="col-md-8 col-md-push-4">
			<h2>Strategy</h2>
			<p>Lehas’  strategy  is  designed  to  create  value  by  leveraging  the company’s many strengths.  These include  its expertise  and experience  in management, the  entity’s highly productive  business units and  a competent staff that is fully endowed to deliver quality services.</p>
		    </div>

		    <div class="col-md-8 col-md-push-4">
			<h2>Vision</h2>
			<p>To become a leader in the provision of quality services in Namibia.</p>
